CatDescriptText: Cutline of related images published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 3, 1962, pg. 14A, reads: "Holiday House Glistens With D.I.'s Style Show and Dancebenefit of MENDS, the National Foundation for Neuromuscular Diseases, Inc."
TitMainTitle: Alberta Thompson wearing skirt tied at waistband, button down blouse, suit jacket with circular brooch, light colored gloves, and tall hat with veil, standing in front of musicians in Holiday House for the D. I. Club's "Melody in Fashion" benefit for MENDS
